  ('real-estate-appraiser-moex-00110', 'real-estate-appraiser', 'real-estate-appraiser-moex-109-5e22d328', 'sub-real-estate-appraiser-03', NULL, 'essay', '不動產機構甲擬投資 10,000萬元購買零售商場作為永續出租經營，現行
