  ('real-estate-appraiser-moex-00118', 'real-estate-appraiser', 'real-estate-appraiser-moex-109-707b521e', 'sub-real-estate-appraiser-05', NULL, 'essay', '依現行相關法令規定，請詳細說明在實施區段徵收範圍內私有土地所有
